# 🪟 KADER Windows Installer

> Install Windows on any KVM Linux VPS in under 30 minutes --- fully
> automated, no ISO, no VNC complexity.


------------------------------------------------------------------------

## 📖 Overview

KADER Windows Installer is a license-based automation tool that installs
Windows on any KVM-based VPS within 10--30 minutes.

It automatically: - Downloads a pre-configured Windows image - Writes it
to the VPS root disk - Configures RDP access - Reboots directly into
Windows

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## ⚡ Features

-   Works on any KVM VPS (Hetzner, Contabo, DigitalOcean, Vultr, Linode,
    OVH, etc.)
-   Supports x86_64 and ARM64
-   7 Windows versions available
-   RDP pre-enabled (port 3389)
-   Fast installation (10--30 minutes)
-   OpenVZ not supported

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## 🚀 Quick Start

### SSH into VPS

``` bash
ssh root@YOUR_VPS_IP
```

### Install Tool

``` bash
curl -o ~/kader.sh https://raw.githubusercontent.com/youngkmd/Freedom/refs/heads/main/installer.sh
chmod +x ~/kader.sh
ln -sf ~/kader.sh /usr/local/bin/k
```

### Run

``` bash
k
```

